Explanations to the reference data

afsis_refdata/afsis_refdata.csv
- total carbon (tc), dry combustion; unit: g/kg	
- total nitrogen (tn), dry combustion; unit: g/kg

cssl_refdata_manuscript_subset/cssl_refdata.csv
- total carbon (tc), dry combustion; unit: g/kg
- total nitrogen (tn), dry combustion; unit: g/kg


cssl_refdata_manuscript_subset/cssl_refdata_all/cssl_refdata_all.csv
- total carbon (tc), dry combustion; unit: g/kg
- total nitrogen (tn), dry combustion; unit: g/kg
- pH measured in H2O (ph_h2o)
- pH measured in KCl (ph_kcl)
- pH measured in CaCl2 (ph_cacl2)
- Clay with particle sizes of 0 - 0.002 mm (clay_0-0.002); unit: %
- Silt with particle sizes 0.002 - 0.05 mm (silt_0.002-0.05); unit: % (USDA classification)
- Silt with particle sizes 0.002 - 0.063 mm (silt_0.002-0.063); unit: % (WRB classification)
- Sand with particle sizpes of 0.05 - 2 mm (sand_0.05-2); unit: % (USDA classification)
- Sand with particle sizes of 0.063 - 2 mm (sand_0.063-2); unit: % (WRB classification)
- Aqua regia extractable cations Al (al_icp), Fe (fe_icp), Ca (ca_icp), Mg (mg_icp), K (k_icp), Mn (mn_icp), Na (na_icp), P (p_icp)
